    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Predicted hemolysis index within 14.3% of experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. RH < 1 acceptance criterion supported by simulation evidence. The CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
